{"tid":322402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無禮貌既人真係做咩都好黑人憎","createTime":"2017-07-14T18:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T19:16:25.000Z","uid":120723,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3f97ce0f35ba3f69325b92c6b7efc0c4d54a7b","tid":322402,"uid":120723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:59:54.000Z","msg":"究竟由幾時開始一個有禮貌嘅人 變到好似稀有種咁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算俾你讀書有幾好 dse再高分<br />\n你份人無禮貌 同人普通對答（例如傾group project 分工/簡單到好似借枝筆呀打招呼個類）<br />\n都要懶係串咁 一係就望你一眼之後唔答<br />\n得罪講句 除非你真係好有才華 都可以叫藝術家脾氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你普普通通正常人一個都咁樣 真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正正常常講句嘢真係好難咩？<br />\n你對人無禮貌 唔好問點解自己大學畢業都搵唔到工<br />\n有冇檢討過自己唔係學歷上唔夠人爭 係個人問題<br />\n仲要有啲帶埋老豆老母見工真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n除非你老豆係上市集團主席 你大撚把錢唔使同人打交道 屋企啲錢夠你食幾世 咁你係有資格咁串<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係我會建議你地重新返幼稚園 學下咩叫禮貌<br />\n唔好再日撚日淨係識背啲深到無人用既英文生字<br />\n然後覺得自己讀名校好撚威 睇唔起其他學生<br />\n香港教育制度淨係注重學術成績 咪搞到有班咁嘅垃圾出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b91501ca74bafea86f100eadca1054e1d650cf","tid":322402,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece80e39dedd4ff8cb0f6f9a77990b53db1e9e52","tid":322402,"uid":120723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4858db1df6a6bb2b619c023835d687d63066ae1f","tid":322402,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87fdae74a6f6735a8457a3c5b08a530b4ff4d18","tid":322402,"uid":120723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}